OL,3,Vupppppp5CThursday                 G1/4
OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FWith the computer system down, the
OL,7,     Fstaff resort to a whiteboard to
OL,8,     Fkeep track of everyone. Patients
OL,9,     Finclude two elderly men with
OL,10,     Fbreathing difficulties.
OL,11,G2100 A&E After Dark
OL,12,     FDoctors treat a non-verbal young
OL,13,     Fman in a life-threatening
OL,14,     Fneurological emergency, while a
OL,15,     Fmidwife with severe spinal pain is
OL,16,     Ffeared to have cauda equina
OL,17,     Fsyndrome after back surgery.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
